parameters.description:
A JSON array of representing the objects to be imported.

These must be structured the same way an import file is structured.

You can import as many item as you want as long as each key MUST have the same name as the column in the corresponding template.

For instance:
```json
 {
    "data_source": {
        "data_source_type": "Comment",
        "data": [
            {
                "commentable/type": "Contract",
                "commentable/key": "id",
                "commentable/value": "46",
                "comment": "Hello world"
            }
        ]
    }
}
```

will add a comment on the Contract with ID 46.
